      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that helpful. a professional is just going to tell me to 'cope' or 'practice mindfulness' or some other bullshit. they don't get the actual weight of it. it's not even a crisis, it's just... a constant, heavy realization that i'm built wrong for this world. like, why am i fighting so hard to stay in a room where i don't even fit? it feels so pointless.",
